title: Kim Kardashian misses her 'babies' North and Saint | Daily Mail Online
text: The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star wore a black corseted tank top that pulled in at her waist and showed some cleavage. She also sported a pair of black drawstring trousers and a brown fur coat. The outing came just a day after husband Kanye West presented his understated Yeezy 5 show in New York City. Kim famously had a traumatizing experience back in October as she was robbed at gunpoint of millions of dollars in jewelry in Paris. Beautiful in burgundy: On Wednesday she was spotted supporting husband Kanye West as he presented his understated Yeezy 5 show in New York City Back-to-back: After the show she was joined by the 39-year-old rapper And according to a Thursday report from People , her 39-year-old rapper husband would like her to attend Paris Fashion Week just months after the incident. The bi-annual high-fashion extravaganza runs February 28 until March 8. It has been added her sister Kendall Jenner will be walking in the runway shows there. It is not known what shows the queen of reality TV will attend, but last year she stopped by Balenciaga, Balmain, Givenchy, and she stopped by the Alai showroom. Kim has not been in Paris since the robbery. Back to France? Earlier in the day it was reported Kim may attention Paris Fashion Week in late February, according to People.
